    }
  ],
  "description": "Complete API testing suite for CORTEX PLATFORM Phase 3 payment integration.\n\n**Quick Start:**\n1. Set BASE_URL to your API endpoint\n2. Run 'Sign Up' → 'Login' (save JWT token)\n3. Run 'Create Order' → save order_id\n4. Run 'Initialize Payment' → visit authorization_url\n5. Complete payment on Paystack test card page\n6. Run 'Verify Payment' to confirm\n7. Use webhook tests to verify backend processing\n\n**Test Card (Paystack):**\n- Number: 4084 0843 0843 0845\n- Expiry: 12/26\n- CVC: 000\n\n**Support:** cortexnexus@proton.me"
}
